<title>USA: United Water Resources Q1 net drops.</title>
<headline>United Water Resources Q1 net drops.</headline>
<dateline>HARRINGTON PARK, N.J. 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr			   $0.12		    $0.15</p>
<p> Net			   4,102		    4,881</p>
<p> Revs			 80,006		   69,759</p>
<p> Avg shrs		   34,741		   33,000</p>
<p>			12 MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr			   $0.97		    $0.66</p>
<p> Net			  33,231		   21,393</p>
<p> Revs			342,292		  319,972</p>
<p> Avg shrs		   34,142		   32,389</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Net includes results from discontinued opers.</p>
<p>Shr from continuing opers is $0.12 vs $0.16 for Q1 and $1.09 vs $0.75 for 12 months.</p>
<p>Q1 1997 net inlcudes 40.05/shr gain from land sale.</p>
<p>Q1 1996 net includes $0.13/shr gain from condemnation settlement.</p>
<p>Q1 net includes charges related to interest and preferred and preference divs of $0.06/shr vs $0.07/shr.</p>
